  "rules": [],
  "notes": "The 'Revenue Protection Priority Level' shown in this flow is that priority level which the RPS is suggesting should be applied to the investigation. Completion of this field is not mandatory.Though all of the address data items included in this flow are defined within the structure as being optional, the address itself is mandatory and must be included in the flow.  The use of any individual address item cannot be made mandatory as, in the absence of an agreed address structure for all flows, an address may be constructed from any combination of the Address Line and Postcode items."
